"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        SymmetricKey objects with different key wrapping data.
        """
a = SymmetricKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, 128, self.bytes_128a,
    key_wrapping_data={})
b = SymmetricKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, 128, self.bytes_128a,
    key_wrapping_data={'wrapping_method': enums.WrappingMethod.ENCRYPT})
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
